predefined_column.comment: The day in the week. Format DDD. Example: mon, tue, wed.

predefined_column.comment: The day number in the week. 1-7 where Sunday is day 1.

predefined_column.comment: The calendar quarter number 1-4.

predefined_column.name: financial_date

predefined_column.name: fin_day_in_week
predefined_column.comment: The financial day in the week. Format DDD. Example: mon,tue,wed.

predefined_column.name: fin_day_in_week_no
predefined_column.comment: Day number in the current financial week.

predefined_column.name: fin_day_in_month
predefined_column.comment: Financial day in the month. Normally the same as calendar day in the month, unless the financial period starts mid calendar month.

predefined_column.comment: Financial day in the year. Number of days since the start of the financial year.

predefined_column.comment: Financial week in the financial month.

predefined_column.name: fin_week_in_year
predefined_column.comment: Financial week in the financial year. Number of weeks since the start of the financial year.

predefined_column.name: fin_month_no
predefined_column.comment: Financial month number. Format MM. Examples: 1,2,3.

predefined_column.name: fin_month
predefined_column.comment: Financial month representation. Format YYYYMM. Examples: 200101, 200102.

predefined_column.name: fin_month_name
predefined_column.comment: Financial month. Format MON. Examples: jan, feb, mar.

predefined_column.name: fin_period
predefined_column.comment: Financial period. Format (YYYY-MM) MON-YYYY. Example: (2001-02) Feb-2002.

predefined_column.name: fin_quarter_no
predefined_column.comment: Financial quarter number (1-4).

predefined_column.name: fin_quarter
predefined_column.comment: Financial quarter representation. Format YYYYQQ. Example: 198901.

predefined_column.name: fin_year
predefined_column.comment: Financial year. Format YYYY.

predefined_column.name: current_cal_day
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate the current day. Normally set to the last day information was updated in the data warehouse.

predefined_column.name: current_cal_week
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate the current week. Set as per current_cal_day.

predefined_column.name: current_cal_month
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate the current month. Set as per current_cal_day.

predefined_column.name: current_cal_year
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate the current year. Set as per current_cal_day.

predefined_column.name: current_cal_mtd
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate days in the current month to date. Set as per current_cal_day.

predefined_column.name: current_cal_ytd
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate days in the current year to date. Set as per current_cal_day.

predefined_column.name: moving_cal_year
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate days that constitute a full year counting back from the current day. Set as per current_cal_day.

predefined_column.name: current_fin_day
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate the current financial day. Normally set to the last financial day information was updated in the data warehouse.

predefined_column.name: current_fin_week
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate the current financial week. Set as per current_fin_day.

predefined_column.name: current_fin_month
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate the current financial month. Set as per current_fin_day.

predefined_column.name: current_fin_quarter
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate the current financial quarter. Set as per current_fin_day.

predefined_column.name: current_fin_year
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate the current financial year. Set as per current_fin_day.

predefined_column.name: current_fin_mtd
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate days in the current financial month to date. Set as per current_fin_day.

predefined_column.name: current_fin_ytd
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate days in the current financial year to date. Set as per current_fin_day.

predefined_column.name: moving_fin_quarter
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate days that constitute a quarter counting back from the current financial day. Set as per current_fin_day.

predefined_column.name: moving_fin_year
predefined_column.comment: Flag to indicate days that constitute a financial year counting back from the current financial day. Set as per current_fin_day.
